data.description: This unique property offers a rare blend of charm, versatility, and endless possibilities. Nestled in the vibrant neighborhood near Huntridge, this property boasts a main home with 3 bedrooms and 1 bath - recently remodeled with LVP flooring, new windows, and updated kitchen. Adjacent to the main home lies an attached casita, complete with a private entrance and convenient kitchenette offering even more flexibility for your lifestyle needs. Whether you dream of a home office, an artist's sanctuary, or a cozy hideaway for relaxation, this additional space provides endless opportunities to customize and create. The detached studio is already rented - meaning this property will start adding value back immediately! Located just moments from historic downtown Las Vegas, you'll enjoy easy access to renowned dining, entertainment, & cultural attractions. Explore the vibrant arts scene, indulge in world-class cuisine, or simply stroll through the charming streets steeped in history!
